description:
This is a 53 minute workout called 'Race Winning Intervals Workout - Indoor Cycle Training' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Competitor vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Subscribe to GCN Training: https://gcn.eu/GCNTraining
